<h2 id="nested">Nested</h2>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-html" data-lang="html">class="alpha" =&gt; first div without margin
class="omega" =&gt; last div without margin</code></pre></figure>

<h2 id="rearrangement">Rearrangement</h2>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-html" data-lang="html">class="push_6" =&gt; last visually(used for changing the order that appear in the HTML)
class="pull_6" =&gt; first visually(used for changing the order that appear in the HTML)</code></pre></figure>

<h2 id="empty-space">Empty space</h2>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-html" data-lang="html">class="prefix_2" =&gt; insert 2 empty columns before
class="suffix_2" =&gt; insert 2 empty columns after</code></pre></figure>

<h2 id="layout">Layout</h2>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-html" data-lang="html">container_XX: 12 or 16 columns</code></pre></figure>
